## Configuration

Configure storage backends in `behest.toml`:

```toml
[stores]
session_backend = "memory"
execution_backend = "memory"
embedding_backend = "memory"
artifact_backend = "memory"

# Or use Redis
[stores]
session_backend = "redis"
execution_backend = "redis"

# Or use PostgreSQL
[stores]
session_backend = "sql"
execution_backend = "sql"
```

