    pub id: Uuid,
    pub title: String,
    pub model: ModelName,
    pub created_at: DateTime<Utc>,
    pub updated_at: DateTime<Utc>,
    pub metadata: Value,
}
```

### MessageRecord

Persisted message exchange:

```rust
